Overview
* Design Responsive UI 
* Used MVVM pattern
* Used SOLID principle approach and clean architecture 
* Used dependency injection
* Used kotlin with min API level 21
* Used Versioning Control i.e. github

Functionalities Done are as follows:

* Consumed API (recommended) using retrofit
* implement splash screen followed by main listing
* listing contain most of the data comes from API
* on click on item a detail popup would appear

Functionality left

* unit testing (Due to time constraints)

